{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wicked Seed blends survival horror elements with an action turn-based combat system. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel through the dark forests of central Maine, explore forgotten underground tunnels, scour an evacuated city, and more as you work to uncover the truth about the sudden appearance of monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/CombatHeader.png?t=1739295480\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Move, block, parry and dodge enemy attacks in real time. Time slows as you queue up your attacks with each subsequent action being stronger than the last. Just make sure to give yourself enough time to get out of harm's way.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1739295480\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/ExplorationHeader.png?t=1739295480\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore off the beaten path and find unique items and upgrades. Decipher hints in notes to solve puzzles and optional tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/ezgif.com-crop__1_.gif?t=1739295480\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/ProgressionHeader.png?t=1739295480\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn XP by killing enemies, exploring new locations, solving puzzles, finding new items, and more to increase your strength. Find new weapons, armor, and accessories to customize your build and playstyle.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/ezgif.com-crop__2_.gif?t=1739295480\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/CostumesHeader.png?t=1739295480\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survive in style with over 30 costumes all completely obtainable through in-game exploration and achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/CostumeCollage.png?t=1739295480\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/extras/FeaturesHeader.png?t=1739295480\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique blend of action and turn-based RPG mechanics with a high skill ceiling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Exploration is always rewarding as it leads to new equipment and permanent stat boosts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All weapons are viable allowing you to use what you want. Power them up through an upgrade system and customize them further using weapon parts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 30 costumes to find and unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlockable difficulties that change up item and enemy placement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Built in randomizer to spice up additional play throughs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find missing costumes or continue to power up through new game plus</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739295480","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739295480","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/ef765153bd4ef739316361389a541cbe94a5647e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739295480","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.a