omizer to spice up additional play throughs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find missing costumes or continue to power up through new game plus</p></li></ul>","developers":["Dead Right Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2767530/header.jpg?t=1739295480","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257089967,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257089967/movie480.mp4?t=1739295478","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257089967/movie_max.mp4?t=1739295478"},"name":"Reveal Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257089967/89b73adbd95484de589907544bb9c3d72c7afd2d/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1739295478","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257089967/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1739295478","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257089967/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1739295478"}}],"name":"Wicked Seed","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Any within the last 5 years<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 16 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GTX 1070+<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 100 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> SSD strongly recommended</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Any within the last 5 years<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 16 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> RTX 2070+<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 200 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> SSD strongly recommended</li><